// Test file for improved branching syntax

BACKGROUND. shop center
CHARACTERS. @Merchant position center

@Merchant Welcome to my shop! What can I get for you?

// New improved branching syntax
CHOICE.
    OPTION. Just browsing, thanks
        @Merchant No problem, take your time!
    END_OPTION.

    OPTION[cost=coins:100] Buy the sword
        @Merchant Excellent choice! Here's your new sword.
